item.title: 718 foxtrot changed ip in loader but friends still cant connect?
item.dc:creator: @pure2ownage Pure_
item.description:
@pure2ownage wrote:

Your machines local IP address may have changed, thus making the portforward rule not work for it. Portforward your local ip address again (you can find your local ip address on network center/probably on your router on a mac filter list or something, with computer names to help you identify yours).
